			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="delete_modal">
		<h1>Delete</h1>
		<p>Are you sure you want to mark this report as not a pothole and delete it?</p>
		<a href="">Yes</a>
		<a href="">No</a>
	</div>
</div>